PresentationTable.name: Time Series
PresentationTable.Description: This folder contains several Period-To-Date and Period-Ago metrics based on Revenue fact.

PresentationColumn.name: 121 ---- Dynamic Time Level ---------------------
PresentationColumn.Description: Help : Header object, dummy not to be used in any queries

PresentationColumn.name: 121 Period Ago Rev
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Dollars physical column in FactsRev table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns data as of previous month vs. month selected in the query.

PresentationColumn.name: 122 Rev Var to Period Ago
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Value change to last month

PresentationColumn.name: 123 Rev Pct Var to Period Ago
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Average % change to last month value

PresentationColumn.name: 125 N Period Agos Rev
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns data as of 2 months before month selected in the query.

PresentationColumn.name: 126 Rev Pct Var to N Period Ago
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Dollars physical column in FactsRev table joining to time using Billed time.
- Average % change to last month value

PresentationColumn.name: 127 ---- Fixed Time Level ---------------------------
PresentationColumn.Description: Help : Header object, dummy not to be used in any queries

PresentationColumn.name: 127 Mth Ago Rev (Fix Time Lvl)
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns data as of previous month vs. month selected in the query.

PresentationColumn.name: 128 Qtr Ago Rev (Fix Time Lvl)
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns Quarter Ago value

PresentationColumn.name: 129 Year Ago Rev (Fix Time Lvl)
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns Year Ago value

PresentationColumn.name: 131 Rev Var to Qtr Ago
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Value change to last quarter

PresentationColumn.name: 132 Rev Pct Var to Qtr Ago
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Difference of the value of the metric in the current period with the value of the metric in the same period the previous quarter / Value of the metric in the same period of the previous quarter

PresentationColumn.name: 133 Rev QAgo Compounded Yrly Gwth
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- % variation to last quarter expressed in a compounded yearly % growth rate.

PresentationColumn.name: 135 Qtr To Dt Rev Sum
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Sums all the values from the first day of the quarter to the current period

PresentationColumn.name: 136 Qtr Ago QTD Rev sum
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Quarter Ago Quarter-To-Date Value for the same period. For the same period in the previous quarter, it returns the sum of all the values from the first day of the quarter to that period.

PresentationColumn.name: 137 QTD Rev Pct Var to Qago QTD
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Average % change of Quarter to date current value to last Quarter quarter to date value
